1
00:00:02,500 --> 00:00:03,140
Huh?

2
00:00:03,270 --> 00:00:04,340
Didn't you make coffee?

3
00:00:04,840 --> 00:00:05,840
Oh, I'm sorry.

4
00:00:05,910 --> 00:00:07,170
I was just making lunch.

5
00:00:07,440 --> 00:00:10,210
All I ask you to do is cook,

6
00:00:10,210 --> 00:00:11,240
which is just an extension of housework.

7
00:00:11,440 --> 00:00:12,880
Your own chores at home...

8
00:00:12,880 --> 00:00:14,610
you should at least do them properly.

9
00:00:14,850 --> 00:00:15,480
Yes.

10
00:00:15,850 --> 00:00:17,850
In a real company,

11
00:00:17,850 --> 00:00:20,420
you'd never make it.

12
00:00:24,060 --> 00:00:27,260
Compared to before we were married,

13
00:00:27,260 --> 00:00:28,700
my husband is like a different person.

14
00:00:29,700 --> 00:00:32,070
My father had me marry him

15
00:00:32,430 --> 00:00:33,970
because he saw the potential

16
00:00:33,970 --> 00:00:35,540
for future growth in the AI industry.

17
00:00:36,840 --> 00:00:37,970
Sorry for the wait.

18
00:00:38,070 --> 00:00:38,910
Here's your hot coffee.

19
00:00:39,070 --> 00:00:40,640
Oh, I'm sorry.

20
00:00:41,070 --> 00:00:42,070
My apologies.

21
00:00:44,380 --> 00:00:46,580
Kaede played the perfect matchmaker,
and that's how we met.

22
00:00:46,580 --> 00:00:48,580
Before we knew it, we were married.

23
00:00:50,080 --> 00:00:51,080
But hey,

24
00:00:52,090 --> 00:00:53,520
to be with someone like me,

25
00:00:53,520 --> 00:00:55,290
someone so talented,

26
00:00:55,320 --> 00:00:58,430
you should feel lucky.

27
00:00:58,530 --> 00:01:01,030
Kaede told me that besides Reika,

28
00:01:01,030 --> 00:01:02,130
he's been involved with many other women.

29
00:01:02,160 --> 00:01:03,330
I've heard reports time and time again.

30
00:01:03,760 --> 00:01:06,400
Before we were married, he was so honest

31
00:01:06,730 --> 00:01:08,200
and passionate about his work.

32
00:01:10,700 --> 00:01:11,700
But...

33
00:01:11,770 --> 00:01:13,740
the more he cheats,

34
00:01:14,140 --> 00:01:16,380
the more relieved I feel.

35
00:01:16,880 --> 00:01:17,880
Because...

36
00:01:17,980 --> 00:01:20,250
my heart belongs only to Reika.

37
00:01:23,680 --> 00:01:27,850
When it comes to his affair,
I'm in no position to say anything.

38
00:01:30,220 --> 00:01:33,190
I decided
we wouldn't see each other again.

39
00:01:33,430 --> 00:01:34,930
But once we meet,

40
00:01:35,330 --> 00:01:35,930
it happens again...

41
00:01:36,200 --> 00:01:38,430
Don't tell me that lunch box...

42
00:01:38,470 --> 00:01:39,800
you copied the recipe for that too?

43
00:01:40,030 --> 00:01:40,470
Huh?

44
00:01:40,870 --> 00:01:42,100
My recipes are...

45
00:01:42,100 --> 00:01:43,700
I know.

46
00:01:44,070 --> 00:01:45,440
They're not copied.

47
00:01:46,770 --> 00:01:48,070
Just messing with you.

48
00:01:50,480 --> 00:01:50,910
But...

49
00:01:51,310 --> 00:01:53,450
with all these plagiarism accusations,
the company's cooking app...

50
00:01:53,450 --> 00:01:56,480
it's a fact that the comment section
is getting flooded.

51
00:01:57,080 --> 00:01:57,950
I'm sorry.

52
00:01:58,080 --> 00:01:59,620
You should be apologizing to the developers.

53
00:01:59,890 --> 00:02:01,420
You need to handle this.

54
00:02:02,420 --> 00:02:05,330
At today's press conference,
explain yourself clearly.

55
00:02:06,000 --> 00:02:07,000
Okay.

56
00:02:07,230 --> 00:02:08,460
At the press conference,

57
00:02:08,700 --> 00:02:09,460
I'm sure Reika will

58
00:02:09,460 --> 00:02:11,160
try to pull something.

59
00:02:12,200 --> 00:02:15,340
You need to apologize properly.

60
00:02:16,070 --> 00:02:17,700
Act like a professional.

61
00:02:17,870 --> 00:02:19,170
Handle it

62
00:02:19,310 --> 00:02:21,340
like a mature adult.
